OL,15,Fmillion shared among departments in
OL,16,Fthe monitoring round, the minister
OL,17,Finsisted he is still #100 million
OL,18,Fshort of the money he needs to make
OL,19,Fpay awards of at least 5.5% to all
OL,20,Fhealth staff.
