OL,4,Coperating at limit, budget document
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FFinance Minister Caoimhe Archibald has
OL,8,Fwarned that, despite the funding boost
OL,9,Ffrom the Chancellor's budget, the
OL,10,Fdevolved administration is still
OL,11,Fovercommitted by around #180 million
OL,12,Facross all departments this year.
OL,14,FShe has made clear that ministers need
OL,15,Fto find more savings and balance the
OL,16,Fbooks.
OL,18,FMr Nesbitt delivered a written
OL,19,Fministerial statement and an updated
OL,20,Fbudget assessment to the Assembly on
OL,21,FThursday.
