OL,4,Coperating at limit, budget document
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FHe said that financial pressures on
OL,8,Fhealth services "remain significant".
OL,10,FMr Nesbitt added: "As the Assembly
OL,11,Fwill be aware, my department is still
OL,12,Fshort of being able to make full 2024/
OL,13,F25 pay settlements in line with those
OL,14,Fin England and Wales.
OL,16,F"I am continuing to actively seek a
OL,17,Fviable solution and I have emphasised
OL,18,Fthat a concerted Executive-wide
OL,19,Fapproach is needed to resolve all NI
OL,20,Fpublic sector pay issues for 2024/25.
